==English==
===Noun===
'''grapple'''
#{{nautical}} a [[device]] consisting of [[iron]] [[claw]]s, attached to the end of a [[rope]], used for [[grasping]] and [[holding]] an [[enemy]] [[ship]] prior to [[boarding]]; a [[grapnel]] or [[grappling iron]]
# the act of [[grappling]]
# a close [[hand-to-hand]] [[struggle]]
===Verb===
'''to grapple'''  (''transitive'')
# to [[seize]] something and [[hold]] it [[firmly]]
'''to grapple'''  (''intransitive'')
# to use a grapple
# to [[wrestle]] or [[tussle]]
